Package: RNILE
Type: Package
Title: Natural Language Information Extraction for Medical Text
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Shuheng Kong, Sinian Zhang
Maintainer: Shuheng Kong <kong0298@umn.edu>
Description: R wrapper for the NILE (Natural Language Information Extraction) Java library
    for processing medical text and extracting semantic objects, modifiers, and locations.
    This package provides functionality to analyze medical reports and extract structured
    information including observations, anatomical locations, and modifiers with
    certainty analysis using the original Java implementation via rJava.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), rJava
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2